title: Personal income in California - income per capita 2000 to 2018
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Income in U.S. dollars, containing a total of 19 data points.
Overall Income in U.S. dollars has increased over the Year.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year '14 and '15.
The highest Income in U.S. dollars, of value 63557.0 was reached at Year '18
The lowest Income in U.S. dollars, of value 33364.0 was reported at Year '00
